{"tid":1512820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嘉道理公開信登報　籲和平解決危機　不應讓年輕人陷絕望","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:13:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7483da0d2a9251cd55b7708f4a4940e1566fe50","tid":1512820,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"中電集團主席米高&middot;嘉道理（Michael Kadoorie）今日在《南華早報》刊登全版廣告。嘉道理以「給香港人的信（A Letter to the People of Hong Kong）」為題發表公開信，指現時香港面臨的情況極具挑戰性，且日益嚴峻，他為此感到痛心。嘉道理表示，暴力不是解決問題的辦法，呼籲香港人和平解決當前的危機。<br />\n<br />\n嘉道理在公開信中形容，其家族與香港有長久的淵源，本港現時的極具挑戰性、且日益嚴峻的情況，令他感到痛心。嘉道理表示自己不支持暴力，因為法治和穩定才是香港賴以成功的基石，他又指，大家一直珍惜的香港精神，正是如何在互相尊重、理解和公開對話的前提下尋求解決問題的辦法。<br />\n<br />\n公開信中指，嘉道理家族在 140 年前到港，這城市為其家族提供了發展的機遇。他引述其先父經常提到香港的獨特之處，是香港將會成為兩套不同意識形態和兩套不同制度的接觸點。<br />\n<br />\n指社會不應讓年輕人絕望<br />\n<br />\n嘉道理強調，自己過往多次提過年輕人是香港的未來，社會不應讓他們陷入絕望中，社會有責任重新建立互信和希望。嘉道理呼籲港人團結，及以堅定不移的決心，為這一代、甚至下一代面對的危機尋求和平解決辦法。<br />\n<br />\n近日多名商界人士及企業相繼在報章刊登聲明，大部分譴責示威者暴力行為，強調香港要盡快止暴制亂，對比下嘉道理聲明明顯較溫和。前公民黨黨魁余若薇在 FB 分享嘉道理公開信時，亦留言：「有心的人從來比有錢的人更有價值」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%98%89%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1-%E7%B1%B2%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E8%AE%93%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%B7%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AE%2593%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25B7%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%2F&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=7ed684bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AE%2593%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25B7%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%2F&h=04a2f516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%98%89%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1-%E7%B1%B2%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E8%AE%93%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%B7%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"b9c05d3f1693507cf90b1975a3b3b64ebc7018a7","tid":1512820,"uid":172443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJotbk4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJotbk4.gif&h=7c162bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99fa470f830b36a798755f72ae6affe7a6cd18cb","tid":1512820,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fe22a7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=9722f262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2Bxp